<paragraph blockId="51.[151,1436,831,966]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,269,832,858]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Remarks:</emphasis>
Allen’s Gallinule 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomson" authorityYear="1842" box="[473,659,832,858]" class="Aves" family="Rallidae" genus="Porphyrio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gruiformes" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alleni">
<emphasis box="[473,659,832,858]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Porphyrio alleni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs in Africa, south of Sahara, 
<collectingCountry box="[1044,1181,831,857]" name="Madagascar" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
, and the 
<collectingCountry box="[1279,1385,832,858]" name="Comoros" pageId="51" pageNumber="52">Comoros</collectingCountry>
, and has been accidental to Europe and Atlantic islands (
<bibRefCitation author="Safford, R. J. &amp; Hawkins, A. F. A." box="[731,1021,867,894]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" refId="ref54791" refString="Safford, R. J. &amp; Hawkins, A. F. A. (2013) The birds of Africa. Volume VIII. The Malagasy Region. Christopher Helm, London, 1024 pp." type="book" year="2013">Safford &amp; Hawkins 2013</bibRefCitation>
). It is an extremely rare visitor to the Mascarenes, with only one record of four birds (one specimen collected and held at UMZC) in 
<date box="[1229,1408,903,930]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" value="1873-12">December 1873</date>
at Oyster Bay, Rodrigues (
<bibRefCitation author="Hartlaub, G." box="[420,586,939,966]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" refId="ref46902" refString="Hartlaub, G. (1877) Die Vogel Madagascar und der benachbarten Insel Gruppen B. H. W. Schmidt, Halle, 425 pp." type="book" year="1877">Hartlaub 1877</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bourne, W. R. P." box="[597,746,939,966]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" pagination="338 - 344" refId="ref42464" refString="Bourne, W. R. P. (1968) The birds of Rodriguez, Indian Ocean. Ibis, 110, 338 - 344. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1474 - 919 X. 1968. tb 00042. x" type="journal article" year="1968">Bourne 1968</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Safford, R. J. &amp; Hawkins, A. F. A." box="[758,1044,939,966]" pageId="51" pageNumber="52" refId="ref54791" refString="Safford, R. J. &amp; Hawkins, A. F. A. (2013) The birds of Africa. Volume VIII. The Malagasy Region. Christopher Helm, London, 1024 pp." type="book" year="2013">Safford &amp; Hawkins 2013</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
